Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,萊登真是個大城市啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 跟我家不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.89,0:00:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,縱橫交錯一不留神就迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,聽說拿到這裡的胸針就好找工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.44,0:00:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好想早點畢業回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.88,0:00:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你只是想要胸針而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.46,0:00:47.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你真壞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:00:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,肅靜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.88,0:01:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,歡迎各位入學自動筆記人偶培訓學校
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.30,0:01:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,第二次遲到就算曠課了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:13.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.77,0:01:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,大戰之後
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.56,0:01:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,對於人偶的需求日益增加
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.38,0:01:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,誠然 即便不在本校就學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.70,0:01:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,也是能夠成為人偶的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.95,0:01:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,但我們不是為了訓練普通的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.63,0:01:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,而是以培養優秀的人偶為目標
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.80,0:01:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,本校的畢業證明就是一流的象徵
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.85,0:01:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 只有我親自認可的優秀人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.27,0:01:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,才能得到這個證明
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.30,0:01:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你們作好心理準備了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:47.03,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.53,0:01:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}薇鷗萊特·艾媧嘉登
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.28,0:01:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}她的行為舉止
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}和她洋娃娃一般的服裝截然不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.36,0:01:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}簡直像軍人一般
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,優秀的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.26,0:03:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,必須要有能把聽到的內容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,準確記錄下來的打字速度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.33,0:03:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 請開始
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.50,0:03:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,艾媧嘉登同學 你怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.16,0:03:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你沒有指定速度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.19,0:03:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我指定了你就能打出來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 就1分鐘200字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.71,0:03:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.76,0:04:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我開始打了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,有請
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你什麼都不吃嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,任務中的飲食應控制到最低限度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我被這麼訓練過
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.27,0:04:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要吃我的嗎 不知道合不合你口味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.75,0:04:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,來自萊登的璐琪莉亞同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.83,0:04:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,你記住我的自我介紹了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人的我都記下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,優秀的人偶應當掌握的書信撰寫技巧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,包括語法和詞彙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,以及各式各樣的書信形式
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:04:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 公布今天的成績
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.44,0:05:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,語法成績
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,滿分 薇鷗萊特·艾媧嘉登
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,下一項 詞彙成績
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.97,0:05:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,滿分 薇鷗萊特·艾媧嘉登
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.59,0:05:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,下官完成任務返回本部報到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.15,0:05:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,學校怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.63,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,被批了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有 並沒有被批評
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.35,0:05:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你回來了啊 薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,社長 請過目
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,這是絡丹瑟教官今天的評價
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.47,0:05:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.46,0:05:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,喔 第一天的評價是優秀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.61,0:05:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喲 你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.46,0:05:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是個男子漢 總是這副死樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.64,0:05:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.27,0:05:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是總這副死樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那兩個人總是這個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,吵個不停
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,社長 真虧你能跟他們倆一起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,開設起我們公司來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:05:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的課程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.94,0:06:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,將就實際的書信代筆進行訓練
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.73,0:06:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.87,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你了 璐琪莉亞同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.97,0:06:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 你要給誰寫信？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.06,0:06:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我想通信的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,寫給你想要表達心意的身邊的人就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,身邊的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.95,0:06:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,收信人是克勞迪婭·霍金斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,克勞迪婭？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.26,0:06:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你朋友？還是家人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是社長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.11,0:06:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,以上 報告完畢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特·艾媧嘉登
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,這就完了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.95,0:06:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,「請問少佐還沒有給我下達新的命令嗎？」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.62,0:06:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,請加上這句話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.33,0:06:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,總覺得這與其說是信 不如說是報告書
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,接下來 請讓我來寫璐琪莉亞同學的信
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.98,0:07:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,不 寫給我父母
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.78,0:07:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,一直沒能好好感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.23,0:07:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,父親母親對我的關愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.87,0:07:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.75,0:07:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,到寫信的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.84,0:07:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,想說的話就說不出口了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 還有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.70,0:07:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我們一起去過的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.47,0:07:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,想要一起去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,有著好多好多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,說不完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.70,0:07:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,請不要擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.13,0:07:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,璐琪莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.62,0:07:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特 你讀讀看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.83,0:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.73,Typing,,0,0,0,,拜上 父親母親大人膝下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.19,0:07:50.34,Typing,,0,0,0,,雖是久未通函 然並無傳達事項
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.66,0:07:53.55,Typing,,0,0,0,,僅就以前的事情未能表達感謝一事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:54.51,Typing,,0,0,0,,時在念中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.27,0:07:56.37,Typing,,0,0,0,,關於一起去過的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.64,0:07:58.16,Typing,,0,0,0,,以及想要一起去的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:00.00,Typing,,0,0,0,,沒有訊息值得向二位轉達
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:03.10,Typing,,0,0,0,,我方現在正銳意努力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:05.53,Typing,,0,0,0,,狀態健康 平安無事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.39,Typing,,0,0,0,,沒有發生問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:08.31,Typing,,0,0,0,,以上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:09.96,Typing,,0,0,0,,請二位勿念
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:10.75,Typing,,0,0,0,,璐琪莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你覺得這就算是信了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.80,0:08:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.31,0:08:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,說不定是怪我說得太抽象了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.60,0:08:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不是這個問題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.93,0:08:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,所謂書信 本就是傳遞人心的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.20,0:08:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,優秀的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是能從說出的話語中間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.49,0:08:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,發現想要傳遞給他人的真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.97,0:08:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你的學習成績優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.37,0:08:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,打字也十分迅速且精確
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.05,0:08:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 你所代筆的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.63,0:08:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不能稱為書信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.99,0:08:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,不能稱為書信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.99,0:08:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,那個 讓我們再…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.11,0:08:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,今天到此為止
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.69,0:08:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 這封信一定要好好交到各自的收信人那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.67,0:08:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,今天你只是狀態不好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.91,0:09:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,以前也被人說過一樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.46,0:09:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.35,0:09:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,吶 讓我告訴你這座城市最棒的景色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.36,0:09:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,小心樓梯很陡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.44,0:09:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,很棒吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.28,0:09:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我從小就
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.87,0:09:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,最喜歡這個風景
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.93,0:09:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好想有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.46,0:10:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,能帶你一起看萊登的那個美景
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.72,0:10:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那我往這邊走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.70,0:10:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,璐琪莉亞同學
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,叫我璐琪莉亞就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.07,0:10:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,夠了 趕緊回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:23.67,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 別這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.79,0:10:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.75,0:10:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥！ 你又喝多了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼？我可沒喝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,請回
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,這傢伙不讓我喝 所以沒喝…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.62,0:10:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.68,0:10:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,該死
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.52,0:10:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,璐琪莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.16,0:10:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.65,0:10:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,很高興你給我寫信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:10:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但這看著怎麼像報告書似的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.39,0:11:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,教官也指出
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.75,0:11:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我所代筆的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.69,0:11:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不能被稱為書信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我能…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,成為優秀的人偶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.47,0:11:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,這就開始做飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.84,0:11:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,父親 母親…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,布魯貝露·尤諾亞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.61,0:11:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:11:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,依貝莉斯·柯諾烏耶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.40,0:12:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,璐琪莉亞·馬爾伯拉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.83,0:12:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,璐琪莉亞·馬爾伯拉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼 以上9名為本次的畢業生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.17,0:12:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,願各位成為優秀的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.75,0:12:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你要去哪做人偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.23,0:12:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去老家的郵局
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.19,0:12:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我大概會在萊登找工作吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.05,0:12:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,璐琪莉亞呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.53,0:12:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,呃 我還什麼都沒想好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.22,0:12:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 你明明是成績第一
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.85,0:12:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊 很遺憾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.75,0:12:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.86,0:12:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不能畢業 也是能當人偶的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.03,0:12:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那我是為什麼去學校學習的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,確實 畢業不是一切
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但要是不能從話語中間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.32,0:12:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,發現想要傳遞給他人的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.93,0:13:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,作為人偶就沒有意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.37,0:13:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就知道你一定會來這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.31,0:13:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,璐琪莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.91,0:13:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,學校已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.61,0:13:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼你會在這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.36,0:13:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我想到這裡來就能再次見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.25,0:13:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,吶 薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.61,0:13:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.32,0:13:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你每次在信最後
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,都一定會加上「少佐還沒有來函嗎？」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.41,0:13:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.95,0:13:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你真正想要寫信的人 是他才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,今天 來給那個人寫封信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,不是平常那種報告書一樣的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,寫一封飽含你真情的書信
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.82,0:13:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我會一直陪著你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,少佐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.86,0:14:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我自己也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,自己想要向他傳遞什麼心意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.73,0:14:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,因為就連他曾經對我說過的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.78,0:14:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,我都還沒有理解
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.60,0:14:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你是為什麼想要成為人偶的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我想理解「我愛你」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.27,0:14:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,想理解…「我愛你」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.63,0:14:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,表達心意是如此困難呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,其實啊 我的父母已經去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.23,0:14:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,還活著的家人 只有哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.11,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 該向哥哥說什麼才好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,自從戰爭開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥作為士兵奔赴沙場
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 他被配置在西部戰線
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.35,0:15:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是個沒什麼戰鬥的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.28,0:15:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,戰爭總是在某個遠離我們的地方發生著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我們總覺得戰爭事不關己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.23,0:15:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 父親跟母親去赫恩從事貿易工作的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.32,0:15:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,西部戰線被突破了的那次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.36,0:15:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,連父親跟母親的遺物都沒找到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,然後 戰爭結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.13,0:15:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥平安回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.92,0:15:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕只有哥哥活下來了 我也很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.47,0:15:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥他很後悔沒能保衛住赫恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,把父親母親的死
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.98,0:16:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,當成是自己的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.47,0:16:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,別讓我再看到你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,其實…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,其實只要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.61,0:16:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,只要他還活著我就足夠開心了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.91,0:16:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,明明只是想要對他說「謝謝」啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.47,0:16:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,卻一直…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.09,0:16:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.30,0:16:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,璐琪莉亞 寫封信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,把你想要表達的心意 寫成信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.36,0:17:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 一想到是要告訴哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.11,0:17:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,就覺得沒用了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.74,0:17:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,迄今為止 不知道有多少次想要告訴他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,可是都沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.33,0:17:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,這次也一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.02,0:17:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝你 薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,給少佐的信 下次再寫吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.12,0:17:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,優秀的人偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是能從說出的話語中間…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.58,0:17:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,發現想要傳遞給他人的真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.36,0:17:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.28,0:17:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}哥哥 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.70,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:17:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}快點 這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.66,0:18:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}真的 好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.83,0:18:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}哇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你是璐琪莉亞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.41,0:18:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,這是？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.65,0:18:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,任務
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,不 這是作業
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.10,0:18:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不 這是信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.43,0:18:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,璐琪莉亞寫給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.94,0:18:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,璐琪莉亞寫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.38,0:19:02.14,Typing,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:07.38,Typing,,0,0,0,,很開心你活下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:11.83,Typing,,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,已經好晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.76,0:19:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪裡了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.37,0:19:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,對了 社長在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.94,0:19:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,說是去行會的聚會了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你學校不是已經結束了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.88,0:19:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.16,0:19:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 今天去寫了一封信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.03,0:19:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然不知道有沒有把心意傳遞到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.20,0:20:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,二位沒有在吵架嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.51,0:20:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就是啊 這個白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.39,0:20:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}把濕杯子放到在我代筆的信上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.64,0:20:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}誰是白痴啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}不都怪你把信放到那種地方！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.35,0:20:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說你怎麼說話的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.36,0:20:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an1}啊 受夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an3}這個態度！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,璐琪莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,早安 薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.20,0:20:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,教官 學校不是已經結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.64,0:20:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起 是我擅自求她的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.32,0:20:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,璐琪莉亞給我看了這封信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.28,0:20:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,你為璐琪莉亞寫給她哥哥的信
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,一直沒能說出口的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.63,0:20:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,對哥哥的心意
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特 是你幫我傳遞給了他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.54,0:20:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,優秀的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.72,0:21:00.09,Default,,0,0,0,,是能從說出的話語中間
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.56,0:21:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,發現想要傳遞給他人的真心的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,如今你已經邁出了這一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.43,0:21:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.25,0:21:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,願你成為優秀的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,薇鷗萊特！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.77,0:21:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,恭喜你！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,璐琪莉亞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.54,0:21:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,真的謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}書信有時
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.17,0:21:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}不需要堆砌浮華的辭藻
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}一句簡單的話語
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.11,0:21:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}就能傳達最真摯的情意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.71,0:21:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}我感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.09,0:21:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}她教會了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.06,0:21:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}作為人偶最重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur6}她是一個穿著洋娃娃一般的服裝
